trans-unit.source: Exchanges are terminated when both the request InputStream and response OutputStream are closed. Closing the OutputStream, implicitly closes the InputStream (if it is not already closed). However, it is recommended to consume all the data from the InputStream before closing it. The convenience method close() does all of these tasks. Closing an exchange without consuming all of the request body is not an error but may make the underlying TCP connection unusable for following exchanges. The effect of failing to terminate an exchange is undefined, but will typically result in resources failing to be freed/reused.
trans-unit.target: 当请求InputStream和响应OutputStream都关闭时，交换终止。关闭OutputStream，隐式关闭InputStream（如果尚未关闭）。但是，建议先关闭InputStream的所有数据，然后再关闭它。便捷方法 close() 完成所有这些任务。在不消耗所有请求主体的情况下关闭交换不是一个错误，但是可能会使基础的TCP连接无法用于后续交换。未能终止交换的影响是不确定的，但是通常会导致资源无法释放/重用。

trans-unit.source: Executes an operation within the context of a particular MethodHandles.Lookup lookup object. Normally, methods on LinkerServices are invoked as part of the linking mechanism in which case Dynalink internally maintains a per-thread current lookup (the one belonging to the descriptor of the call site being linked). This lookup can be retrieved by any GuardingTypeConverterFactory involved in linking if it needs to generate lookup-sensitive converters. However, linker services' methods can be invoked outside the linking process too when implementing invocation-time dispatch schemes, invoking conversions at runtime, etc. If it becomes necessary to use any type converter in this situation, and it needs a lookup, it will normally only get MethodHandles.publicLookup() as the thread is not engaged in a linking operation. If there is a way to meaningfully associate the operation to the context of some caller class, consider performing it within an invocation of this method and passing a full-strength lookup for that class, as it will associate that lookup with the current thread for the duration of the operation. Note that since you are passing a SecureLookupSupplier, any invoked type converter factories will still need to hold the necessary runtime permission to be able to get the lookup should they need it.
trans-unit.target: 在特定 MethodHandles.Lookup 查找对象的上下文中执行操作。通常， LinkerServices 上的方法作为链接机制的一部分被调用，在这种情况下，Dynalink在内部维护每线程的当前查找（属于要链接的调用站点的描述符的查找）。如果需要生成对查找敏感的转换器，则可以由链接中涉及的任何 GuardingTypeConverterFactory 检索此查找。但是，在实现调用时分派方案，在运行时调用转换时，也可以在链接过程之外调用链接器服务的方法。如果在这种情况下有必要使用任何类型转换器，并且需要查找，它将通常只能得到 MethodHandles.publicLookup() ,因为线程未参与链接操作。如果有一种方法可以将操作与某个调用者类的上下文有意义地关联，请考虑在此方法的调用中执行该操作并传递该类的全强度查找，因为它将该查找与当前线程相关联。手术持续时间。请注意，由于您正在传递 SecureLookupSupplier ，因此任何调用的类型转换器工厂仍将需要持有必要的运行时权限，以便能够在需要时获取查找。

trans-unit.source: Exported remote objects receive method invocations from the stubs as described in the RMI specification. Each invocation's operation and parameters are unmarshaled using a custom ObjectInputStream. If an ObjectInputFilter is provided and is not null when the object is exported, it is used to filter the parameters as they are unmarshaled from the stream. The filter is used for all invocations and all parameters regardless of the method being invoked or the parameter values. If no filter is provided or is null for the exported object then the ObjectInputStream default filter, if any, is used. The default filter is configured with ObjectInputFilter.Config.setSerialFilter. If the filter rejects any of the parameters, the InvalidClassException thrown by ObjectInputStream is reported as the cause of an UnmarshalException.
trans-unit.target: 如RMI规范中所述，导出的远程对象从存根接收方法调用。每次调用的操作和参数都使用自定义 ObjectInputStream 解组。如果提供了 ObjectInputFilter ，并且在导出对象时不为 null ，则将其用于过滤从流中取消编组的参数。该过滤器用于所有调用和所有参数，而与调用的方法或参数值无关。如果没有提供过滤器，或者对于导出的对象为 null ，则使用 ObjectInputStream 默认过滤器（如果有）。默认过滤器是使用 ObjectInputFilter.Config.setSerialFilter 配置的。如果过滤器拒绝任何参数，则将 ObjectInputStream 抛出的 InvalidClassException 报告为 UnmarshalException 的原因。

trans-unit.source: Factory methods that produce or lookup VarHandle instances document the set of access modes that are supported, which may also include documenting restrictions based on the variable type and whether a variable is read-only. If an access mode is not supported then the corresponding access mode method will on invocation throw an UnsupportedOperationException. Factory methods should document any additional undeclared exceptions that may be thrown by access mode methods. The get access mode is supported for all VarHandle instances and the corresponding method never throws UnsupportedOperationException. If a VarHandle references a read-only variable (for example a final field) then write, atomic update, numeric atomic update, and bitwise atomic update access modes are not supported and corresponding methods throw UnsupportedOperationException. Read/write access modes (if supported), with the exception of get and set, provide atomic access for reference types and all primitive types. Unless stated otherwise in the documentation of a factory method, the access modes get and set (if supported) provide atomic access for reference types and all primitives types, with the exception of long and double on 32-bit platforms.
trans-unit.target: 产生或 lookup VarHandle实例的工厂方法记录了所支持的访问模式集，其中还可能包括记录基于变量类型和变量是否为只读的限制。如果不支持访问模式，则相应的访问模式方法将在调用时抛出 UnsupportedOperationException 。工厂方法应记录访问模式方法可能引发的任何其他未声明的异常。该 get 支持所有VarHandle实例访问模式和相应的方法从不抛出 UnsupportedOperationException 异常。如果VarHandle引用了只读变量（例如 final 字段），然后不支持写，原子更新，数字原子更新和按位原子更新访问模式，并且相应的方法将抛出 UnsupportedOperationException 。除了 get 和 set 之外，读/写访问模式（如果支持）提供对引用类型和所有基本类型的原子访问。除非在工厂方法的文档中另有说明，否则 get 和 set 访问方式（如果支持）为引用类型和所有基本类型提供原子访问，但32位平台上的 long 和 double 除外。

trans-unit.source: Fetches a tag constant for a well-known tag name (i.e. one of the tags in the set {A, ADDRESS, APPLET, AREA, B, BASE, BASEFONT, BIG, BLOCKQUOTE, BODY, BR, CAPTION, CENTER, CITE, CODE, DD, DFN, DIR, DIV, DL, DT, EM, FONT, FORM, FRAME, FRAMESET, H1, H2, H3, H4, H5, H6, HEAD, HR, HTML, I, IMG, INPUT, ISINDEX, KBD, LI, LINK, MAP, MENU, META, NOBR, NOFRAMES, OBJECT, OL, OPTION, P, PARAM, PRE, SAMP, SCRIPT, SELECT, SMALL, SPAN, STRIKE, S, STRONG, STYLE, SUB, SUP, TABLE, TD, TEXTAREA, TH, TITLE, TR, TT, U, UL, VAR}. trans-unit.source: Fetches all of the actions defined in this keymap.
trans-unit.target: 获取该键图中定义的所有动作。

trans-unit.source: Fetches all of the keystrokes in this map that are bound to some action.
trans-unit.target: 获取此地图中所有绑定到某个动作的按键。

trans-unit.source: Fetches an attribute constant for a well-known attribute name (i.e. one of the attributes in the set {FACE, COMMENT, SIZE, COLOR, CLEAR, BACKGROUND, BGCOLOR, TEXT, LINK, VLINK, ALINK, WIDTH, HEIGHT, ALIGN, NAME, HREF, REL, REV, TITLE, TARGET, SHAPE, COORDS, ISMAP, NOHREF, ALT, ID, SRC, HSPACE, VSPACE, USEMAP, LOWSRC, CODEBASE, CODE, ARCHIVE, VALUE, VALUETYPE, TYPE, CLASS, STYLE, LANG, DIR, DECLARE, CLASSID, DATA, CODETYPE, STANDBY, BORDER, SHAPES, NOSHADE, COMPACT, START, ACTION, METHOD, ENCTYPE, CHECKED, MAXLENGTH, MULTIPLE, SELECTED, ROWS, COLS, DUMMY, CELLSPACING, CELLPADDING, VALIGN, HALIGN, NOWRAP, ROWSPAN, COLSPAN, PROMPT, HTTPEQUIV, CONTENT, LANGUAGE, VERSION, N, FRAMEBORDER, MARGINWIDTH, MARGINHEIGHT, SCROLLING, NORESIZE, MEDIA, ENDTAG}).
trans-unit.target: 获取一个著名属性名的属性常量(即 FACE,COMMENT,SIZE,COLOR,CLEAR,BACKGROUND,BGCOLOR,TEXT,LINK,VLINK,ALINK,WIDTH,HEIGHT,ALIGN,NAME,HREF,REL,REV,TITLE,TARGET,SHAPE,COORDS,ISMAP,NOHREF,ALT,ID,SRC,HSPACE,VSPACE,USEMAP,LOWSRC,CODEBASE,CODE,ARCHIVE,VALUE,VALUETYPE,TYPE,CLASS,STYLE,LANG,DIR,DECLARE,CLASSID。DATA,CODETYPE,STANDBY,BORDER,SHAPES,NOSHADE,COMPACT,START,ACTION,METHOD,ENCTYPE,CHECKED,MAXLENGTH,MULTIPLE,SELECTED,ROWS,COLS,DUMMY,CELLSPACING,CELLPADDING,VALIGN,HALIGN,NOWRAP,ROWSPAN,COLSPAN,PROMPT,HTTPEQUIV,CONTENT,LANGUAGE,VERSION,N,FRAMEBORDER,MARGINWIDTH,MARGINHEIGHT,SCROLLING,NORESIZE,MEDIA,ENDTAG})。)

trans-unit.source: Fetches an attribute constant for a well-known attribute name (i.e. one of the attributes in the set {FACE, COMMENT, SIZE, COLOR, CLEAR, BACKGROUND, BGCOLOR, TEXT, LINK, VLINK, ALINK, WIDTH, HEIGHT, ALIGN, NAME, HREF, REL, REV, TITLE, TARGET, SHAPE, COORDS, ISMAP, NOHREF, ALT, ID, SRC, HSPACE, VSPACE, USEMAP, LOWSRC, CODEBASE, CODE, ARCHIVE, VALUE, VALUETYPE, TYPE, CLASS, STYLE, LANG, DIR, DECLARE, CLASSID, DATA, CODETYPE, STANDBY, BORDER, SHAPES, NOSHADE, COMPACT, START, ACTION, METHOD, ENCTYPE, CHECKED, MAXLENGTH, MULTIPLE, SELECTED, ROWS, COLS, DUMMY, CELLSPACING, CELLPADDING, VALIGN, HALIGN, NOWRAP, ROWSPAN, COLSPAN, PROMPT, HTTPEQUIV, CONTENT, LANGUAGE, VERSION, N, FRAMEBORDER, MARGINWIDTH, MARGINHEIGHT, SCROLLING, NORESIZE, MEDIA, ENDTAG}). If the given name does not represent one of the well-known attributes, then null will be returned.
trans-unit.target: 获取知名属性名称的属性常量（即，集合{FACE，COMMENT，SIZE，COLOR，CLEAR，BACKGROUND，BGCOLOR，TEXT，LINK，VLINK，ALINK，WIDTH，HEIGHT，ALIGN，NAME中的属性之一） ，HREF，REL，REV，标题，目标，形状，坐标，ISMAP，NOHREF，ALT，ID，SRC，HSPACE，VSPACE，USEMAP，LOWSRC，CODEBASE，CODE，ARCHIVE，VALUE，VALUE类型，TYPE，CLASS，STYLE，LANG ，DIR，DECLARE，CLASSID，DATA，CODETYPE，STANDBY，BORDER，SHAPES，NOSHADE，COMPACT，START，ACTION，方法，ENCTYPE，CHECKED，MAXLENGTH，多个，选择，ROWS，COLS，DUMMY，CELLSPACING，CELLPADDING，VALIGN，HALIGN ，NOWRAP，ROWSPAN，COLSPAN，PROMPT，HTTPEQUIV，CONTENT，语言，VERSION，N，FRAMEBORDER，MARGINWIDTH，MARGINHEIGHT，SCROLLING，NORESIZE，MEDIA，ENDTAG}）。如果给定名称不代表众所周知的属性之一，则 null 将返回null。

trans-unit.source: Fetches an empty AttributeSet.
trans-unit.target: 获取一个空的AttributeSet。

trans-unit.source: Fetches an integer attribute value.
trans-unit.target: 获取一个整数属性值。

trans-unit.source: Fetches an integer attribute value. Attribute values are stored as a string, and this is a convenience method to convert to an actual integer.
trans-unit.target: 获取一个整数属性值。属性值以字符串的形式存储,这是一种方便的方法,可以将其转换为实际的整数。

trans-unit.source: Fetches an iterator for the specified HTML tag.
trans-unit.target: 获取指定HTML标签的迭代器。

trans-unit.source: Fetches an iterator for the specified HTML tag. This can be used for things like iterating over the set of anchors contained, or iterating over the input elements.
trans-unit.target: 获取指定HTML标签的迭代器。这个迭代器可以用来迭代包含的锚点集,或者迭代输入元素。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the FontMetrics used for this view.
trans-unit.target: 获取用于此视图的 FontMetrics 。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the StyleSheet with the document-specific display rules (CSS) that were specified in the HTML document itself.
trans-unit.target: 使用在HTML文档本身中指定的文档特定的显示规则（CSS）来获取 StyleSheet 。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the ViewFactory implementation that is feeding the view hierarchy.
trans-unit.target: 获取正在馈送视图层次结构的 ViewFactory 实现。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the ViewFactory implementation that is feeding the view hierarchy. Normally the views are given this as an argument to updates from the model when they are most likely to need the factory, but this method serves to provide it at other times.
trans-unit.target: 获取正在馈送视图层次结构的 ViewFactory 实现。通常，在最有可能需要工厂的情况下，将视图作为参数从模型进行更新，但这是在其他时间提供的方法。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the EditorKit for the UI.
trans-unit.target: 获取UI的EditorKit。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the EditorKit for the UI. This is whatever is currently set in the associated JEditorPane.
trans-unit.target: 获取UI的EditorKit。这是当前在关联的JEditorPane中设置的任何内容。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the ElementIterator.
trans-unit.target: 获取ElementIterator。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the action appropriate for the given symbolic event sequence.
trans-unit.target: 获取适合给定符号事件序列的动作。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the action appropriate for the given symbolic event sequence. This is used by JTextController to determine how to interpret key sequences. If the binding is not resolved locally, an attempt is made to resolve through the parent keymap, if one is set.
trans-unit.target: 获取适合给定符号事件序列的动作。这被JTextController用来决定如何解释键序列。如果绑定没有在本地解析,则会尝试通过父键图(如果设置了)解析。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the allocation for the given child view to render into.
trans-unit.target: 获取给定子视图的渲染分配。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the allocation for the given child view to render into. This enables finding out where various views are located.
trans-unit.target: 获取要渲染到的给定子视图的分配。这可以找出各种视图的位置。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the allocation for the given child view.
trans-unit.target: 获取给定子视图的分配。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the allocation for the given child view. This enables finding out where various views are located, without assuming how the views store their location. This returns null since the default is to not have any child views.
trans-unit.target: 获取给定子视图的分配。这使得能够找出各种视图的位置，而无需假设视图如何存储它们的位置。由于默认情况下没有任何子视图，因此返回 null 。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the allocation for the given child view. This enables finding out where various views are located, without assuming the views store their location. This returns null since the default is to not have any child views.
trans-unit.target: 获取给定子视图的分配。这可以找出各种视图的位置,而不需要假设视图存储它们的位置。这将返回null,因为默认情况是没有任何子视图。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the allocation for the given child view. This enables finding out where various views are located. This is implemented to return null if the layout is invalid, otherwise the superclass behavior is executed.
trans-unit.target: 获取给定子视图的分配。这样可以找出各种视图的位置。如果布局无效，则实现此方法以返回 null ，否则将执行超类行为。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the attributes to use when rendering.
trans-unit.target: 获取渲染时要使用的属性。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the attributes to use when rendering. By default this simply returns the attributes of the associated element. This method should be used rather than using the element directly to obtain access to the attributes to allow view-specific attributes to be mixed in or to allow the view to have view-specific conversion of attributes by subclasses. Each view should document what attributes it recognizes for the purpose of rendering or layout, and should always access them through the AttributeSet returned by this method.
trans-unit.target: 获取渲染时要使用的属性。默认情况下，这仅返回关联元素的属性。应该使用此方法，而不是直接使用元素来获取对属性的访问权限，以允许将视图特定的属性混入其中或允许视图通过子类进行视图特定的属性转换。每个视图都应记录其可识别的属性以进行渲染或布局，并应始终通过此方法返回的 AttributeSet 对其进行访问。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the attributes to use when rendering. This is implemented to multiplex the attributes specified in the model with a StyleSheet.
trans-unit.target: 获取渲染时要使用的属性。这实现了在模型中指定的属性与StyleSheet的复用。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the axis along which views should be flowed.
trans-unit.target: 获取视图流向的轴。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the axis along which views should be flowed. By default, this will be the axis orthogonal to the axis along which the flow rows are tiled (the axis of the default flow rows themselves). This is typically used by the FlowStrategy.
trans-unit.target: 获取视图应沿其流动的轴。默认情况下，这将是与流行平铺的轴（默认流行本身的轴）正交的轴。这通常由 FlowStrategy 使用。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the background color to use to render the glyphs.
trans-unit.target: 获取用于渲染字形的背景色。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the background color to use to render the glyphs. This is implemented to return a cached background color, which defaults to null.
trans-unit.target: 获取用于渲染字形的背景颜色。实现此方法以返回缓存的背景色，默认为 null 。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the binding of services that set a policy for the type of document being edited.
trans-unit.target: 获取为正在编辑的文档类型设置策略的服务的绑定。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the binding of services that set a policy for the type of document being edited. This contains things like the commands available, stream readers and writers, etc.
trans-unit.target: 获取为正在编辑的文档类型设置策略的服务的绑定。这包含了可用的命令、流式读写器等内容。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the box formatter to use for the given set of CSS attributes.
trans-unit.target: 获取要用于给定CSS属性集的盒子格式化器。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the caret that allows text-oriented navigation over the view.
trans-unit.target: 获取允许在视图上进行文本导航的插图。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the character attributes in effect at the current location of the caret, or null.
trans-unit.target: 获取在插入符号的当前位置有效的字符属性，或者为 null 。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the child element at the given index.
trans-unit.target: 在给定的索引中获取子元素。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the child view at the given coordinates.
trans-unit.target: 在给定坐标处获取子视图。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the child view index at the given point.
trans-unit.target: 获取指定点的子视图索引。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the child view index at the given point. This is called by the various View methods that need to calculate which child to forward a message to. This should be called by a block synchronized on this object, and would typically be followed with one or more calls to getChildAllocation that should also be in the synchronized block.
trans-unit.target: 获取给定点的子视图索引。这被需要计算将消息转发到哪个子节点的各种View方法所调用。这应该由在这个对象上同步的区块来调用,通常会有一个或多个getChildAllocation的调用,这些调用也应该在同步的区块中。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the child view index representing the given position in the model.
trans-unit.target: 获取代表模型中给定位置的子视图索引。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the child view index representing the given position in the model. This is implemented to fetch the view in the case where there is a child view for each child element.
trans-unit.target: 获取代表模型中给定位置的子视图索引。在每个子元素都有一个子视图的情况下,实现这个功能是为了获取视图。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the child view that represents the given position in the model.
trans-unit.target: 获取代表模型中给定位置的子视图。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the child view that represents the given position in the model. This is implemented to fetch the view in the case where there is a child view for each child element.
trans-unit.target: 获取代表模型中给定位置的子视图。在每个子元素都有子视图的情况下,实现这个功能是为了获取视图。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the child view that represents the given position in the model. This is implemented to walk through the children looking for a range that contains the given position. In this view the children do not necessarily have a one to one mapping with the child elements.
trans-unit.target: 获取代表模型中给定位置的子视图。这实现了在子视图中寻找包含给定位置的范围。在这个视图中,子元素不一定与子元素有一对一的映射。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the collection of attributes this element contains.
trans-unit.target: 获取该元素包含的属性集合。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the command list for the editor.
trans-unit.target: 获取编辑器的命令列表。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the command list for the editor. This is the list of commands supported by the plugged-in UI augmented by the collection of commands that the editor itself supports. These are useful for binding to events, such as in a keymap.
trans-unit.target: 获取编辑器的命令列表。这是由插入式用户界面支持的命令列表,并由编辑器本身支持的命令集合增强。这些命令对于绑定事件很有用,比如在键盘图中。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the command list for the editor. This is the list of commands supported by the superclass augmented by the collection of commands defined locally for style operations.
trans-unit.target: 获取编辑器的命令列表。这是由超类支持的命令列表,由本地定义的样式操作命令集合增强。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the constraining span to flow against for the given child index.
trans-unit.target: 获取给定子索引的约束跨度。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the container hosting the view.
trans-unit.target: 获取承载视图的容器。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the container hosting the view. This is useful for things like scheduling a repaint, finding out the host components font, etc. The default implementation of this is to forward the query to the parent view.
trans-unit.target: 获取承载视图的容器。这对于调度重绘、找出主机组件的字体等事情很有用。默认的实现是将查询转发给父视图。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the context for managing attributes.
trans-unit.target: 获取管理属性的上下文。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the context for managing attributes. This method effectively establishes the strategy used for compressing AttributeSet information.
trans-unit.target: 获取管理属性的上下文。该方法有效地建立了用于压缩AttributeSet信息的策略。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the current Element.
trans-unit.target: 获取当前的 Element 。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the current Element.
trans-unit.target: 获取当前元素。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the current color used to render the caret.
trans-unit.target: 获取当前用于渲染圆点的颜色。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the current color used to render the disabled text.
trans-unit.target: 获取当前用于渲染禁用文本的颜色。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the current color used to render the selected text.
trans-unit.target: 获取当前用于渲染选定文本的颜色。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the current color used to render the selection.
trans-unit.target: 获取当前用于渲染选区的颜色。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the current depth of element tree.
trans-unit.target: 获取当前元素树的深度。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the current list of highlights.
trans-unit.target: 获取当前的亮点列表。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the current offset within the document.
trans-unit.target: 获取文档中的当前偏移量。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the current paragraph attributes in effect at the location of the caret, or null if none.
trans-unit.target: 获取在插入符号位置有效的当前段落属性；如果没有，则为 null 。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the current position of the caret.
trans-unit.target: 获取caret的当前位置。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the current position of the mark.
trans-unit.target: 获取标记的当前位置。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the current position of the mark. If there is a selection, the dot and mark will not be the same.
trans-unit.target: 获取标记的当前位置。如果有选择,则点和标记将不一致。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the current position of the mark. If there is a selection, the mark will not be the same as the dot.
trans-unit.target: 获取当前标记的位置。如果有选择,则标记与点的位置不一致。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the current writing thread if there is one.
trans-unit.target: 如果有写线程,则获取当前的写线程。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the current writing thread if there is one. This can be used to distinguish whether a method is being called as part of an existing modification or if a lock needs to be acquired and a new transaction started.
trans-unit.target: 获取当前的写线程(如果有的话)。这可以用来区分一个方法是否作为现有修改的一部分被调用,或者是否需要获取一个锁并启动一个新的事务。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the currently installed kit for handling content.
trans-unit.target: 获取当前安装的处理内容的套件。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the currently installed kit for handling content. createDefaultEditorKit is called to set up a default if necessary.
trans-unit.target: 获取当前安装的用于处理内容的工具包。如果需要，将调用 createDefaultEditorKit 设置默认值。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the default action to fire if a key is typed (i.e. a KEY_TYPED KeyEvent is received) and there is no binding for it.
trans-unit.target: 如果键被键入(即收到KEY_TYPED KeyEvent)且没有绑定,则获取默认的动作。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the default action to fire if a key is typed (i.e. a KEY_TYPED KeyEvent is received) and there is no binding for it. Typically this would be some action that inserts text so that the keymap doesn't require an action for each possible key.
trans-unit.target: 如果键被键入(即收到KEY_TYPED KeyEvent)且没有绑定,则获取默认动作。通常这将是一些插入文本的操作,这样键位图就不需要为每个可能的键位提供操作。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the document associated with this element.
trans-unit.target: 获取与该元素相关的文档。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the document.
trans-unit.target: 获取文档。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the editor kit to use for the given type of content.
trans-unit.target: 获取给定内容类型的编辑包。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the editor kit to use for the given type of content. This is called when a type is requested that doesn't match the currently installed type. If the component doesn't have an EditorKit registered for the given type, it will try to create an EditorKit from the default EditorKit registry. If that fails, a PlainEditorKit is used on the assumption that all text documents can be represented as plain text.
trans-unit.target: 获取用于给定类型的内容的编辑器工具包。当请求的类型与当前安装的类型不匹配时，将调用此方法。如果组件没有为给定类型注册的 EditorKit ，它将尝试从默认的 EditorKit 注册表中创建一个 EditorKit 。如果失败，则假定所有文本文档都可以表示为纯文本， PlainEditorKit 使用PlainEditorKit。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the element representing the current run of character attributes for the caret.
trans-unit.target: 获取代表当前cart的字符属性运行的元素。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the first element.
trans-unit.target: 获取第一个元素。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the inset needed on a given side to account for the margin, border, and padding.
trans-unit.target: 获取给定面所需的镶边,以考虑到边距、边框和padding。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the keymap currently active in this text component.
trans-unit.target: 获取该文本组件中当前活动的键图。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the keystrokes that will result in the given action.

trans-unit.target: 获取逻辑选择的另一端的位置。如果没有选择,则与点的位置相同。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the location of the caret.
trans-unit.target: 获取caret的位置。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the logical style assigned to the paragraph represented by the current position of the caret, or null.

trans-unit.source: Fetches the model associated with the view.
trans-unit.target: 获取与视图相关联的模型。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the name of the element.
trans-unit.target: 获取元素的名称。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the name of the element. If the element is used to represent some type of structure, this would be the type name.
trans-unit.target: 获取元素的名称。如果该元素是用来表示某种结构类型,则为类型名。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the name of the keymap that will be installed/used by default for this UI.
trans-unit.target: 获取该用户界面默认安装/使用的keymap的名称。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the name of the keymap that will be installed/used by default for this UI. This is implemented to create a name based upon the classname. The name is the name of the class with the package prefix removed.
trans-unit.target: 获取默认安装的keymap的名称。这是为创建一个基于类名的名称而实现的。这个名称是去掉包前缀的类的名称。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the name of the set of key-bindings.
trans-unit.target: 获取密钥绑定集的名称。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the name of the style.
trans-unit.target: 获取样式的名称。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the name of the style. A style is not required to be named, so null is returned if there is no name associated with the style.
trans-unit.target: 获取样式的名称。不需要命名样式，因此，如果没有与样式相关联的名称，则返回 null 。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the name of the style. A style is not required to be named, so null is returned if there is no name associated with the style.
trans-unit.target: 获取样式的名称。样式不需要命名,如果没有与样式相关联的名称,则返回null。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the next Element.

trans-unit.source: Fetches the offset from the beginning of the document that this element begins at. If this element has children, this will be the offset of the first child. As a document position, there is an implied forward bias.

trans-unit.target: 获取该元素从文档开始到结束的偏移量。如果这个元素有子元素,那么这将是最后一个子元素的结束偏移量。作为文档的位置,有一个隐含的向后的偏移。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the offset of a particular child's current layout.
trans-unit.target: 获取特定子代当前布局的偏移量。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the reader for the parser to use when loading the document with HTML. This is implemented to return an instance of HTMLDocument.HTMLReader. Subclasses can reimplement this method to change how the document gets structured if desired. (For example, to handle custom tags, or structurally represent character style elements.)
trans-unit.target: 获取读取器以供分析器在使用HTML加载文档时使用。实现它是为了返回 HTMLDocument.HTMLReader 的实例。子类可以重新实现此方法，以根据需要更改文档的结构方式。（例如，处理自定义标签或在结构上表示字符样式元素。）

trans-unit.source: Fetches the text component that currently has focus. This allows actions to be shared across text components which is useful for key-bindings where a large set of actions are defined, but generally used the same way across many different components.
trans-unit.target: 获取当前有焦点的文本组件。这允许文本组件之间共享动作,这对于定义了大量动作,但通常在许多不同组件中以相同方式使用的键绑定非常有用。

trans-unit.target: 获取平铺轴属性。这是子视图被平铺的轴。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the user-interface factory for this text-oriented editor.
trans-unit.target: 获取这个面向文本的编辑器的用户界面工厂。

trans-unit.source: Fetches the value of the given attribute. If the value is not found locally, the search is continued upward through the resolving parent (if one exists) until the value is either found or there are no more parents. If the value is not found, null is returned.
trans-unit.target: 获取给定属性的值。如果在本地没有找到值,则通过解析父代(如果存在)继续向上搜索,直到找到值或没有父代为止。如果没有找到值,则返回null。

trans-unit.source: Few guarantees can be made regarding node creation. Because nodes are created implicitly upon access, it may not be feasible for an implementation to determine whether a child node existed in the backing store prior to access (for example, because the backing store is unreachable or cached information is out of date). Under these circumstances, implementations are neither required to generate node change events nor prohibited from doing so.
trans-unit.target: 对于节点的创建,几乎没有什么保证。因为节点是在访问时隐含地创建的,所以实施者可能无法确定子节点在访问前是否存在于后盾存储中(例如,因为后盾存储无法访问或缓存信息已经过时)。在这些情况下,既不要求实施者生成节点变化事件,也不禁止实施者这样做。
